235
00:25:48,340 --> 00:25:50,760
<i>...berarti peperangan berhenti.</i>

236
00:25:50,850 --> 00:25:52,010
<i>Namun pada perang gerilya,...</i>

237
00:25:52,100 --> 00:25:56,310
<i>...jika satu pihak mungkin
